website_description: APR Supply Co is as a full service distributor of Plumbing, HVAC, PVF, and Hydronic supplies since 1922. You can visit anyone of our 38 branch locations or 9 showroom locations to view our products and learn more about the services that we offer. We pride ourselves on providing our customers with the highest quality products and services in the industry. APR Supply Co. has been built on a foundation of five principal, core values: Customer, Excellence, Integrity, Respect, and Results. We focus and stress putting you, our Customer first. This allows us to provide you with the correct product or service in a timely manner. Through our efforts within Excellence, our central distribution center is able to offer you next day delivery, a large inventory, and an order accuracy rate of over 99.5%. By operating with Integrity and Respect, we establish and maintain great relationships with our customers and our vendors by showcasing our strong work ethic and willingness to do the right thing. APR Supply Co. is a third generation wholesaler that grew from the development of the Lebanon Plumbing Supply Co. After working at the Lebanon Plumbing Supply Co. for 13 years, Mark Tice purchased the controlling interest of the company in 1947. In 1975, Mark’s son Randy Tice joined the industry, launching his own controls business, Environmental Equipment Engineering Co. The two companies merged in 1982 to form APR Supply Co. Present day, APR Supply Co. has over 320 employees, the majority located at the central distribution center and corporate headquarters in Lebanon, PA.

APR Supply Co. has been built on a foundation of five principal, core values: Customer, Excellence, Integrity, Respect, and Results. We focus and stress putting you, our Customer first. After working at the Lebanon Plumbing Supply Co. for 13 years, Mark Tice purchased the controlling interest of the company in 1947. In 1975, Mark’s son Randy Tice joined the industry, launching his own controls business, Environmental Equipment Engineering Co. The two companies merged in 1982 to form APR Supply Co. website_description: APR Supply Co is as a full service distributor of Plumbing, HVAC, PVF, and Hydronic supplies since 1922. We work with contractors throughout Pennsylvania, New York, New Jersey and Delaware to help our customers service their customers. You can visit anyone of our 38 branch locations or 9 showroom locations to view our products and learn more about the services that we offer. We pride ourselves on providing our customers with the highest quality products and services in the industry. APR Supply Co. has been built on a foundation of five principal, core values: Customer, Excellence, Integrity, Respect, and Results. We focus and stress putting you, our Customer first. This allows us to provide you with the correct product or service in a timely manner. Through our efforts within Excellence, our central distribution center is able to offer you next day delivery, a large inventory, and an order accuracy rate of over 99.5%. By operating with Integrity and Respect, we establish and maintain great relationships with our customers and our vendors by showcasing our strong work ethic and willingness to do the right thing. By combining our efforts in putting the Customer first, providing product and service Excellence, and operating with Integrity and Respect, we achieve the Results that you are looking for, and we achieve our company mission: Creating Enthusiastic Customers! APR Supply Co. is a third generation wholesaler that grew from the development of the Lebanon Plumbing Supply Co. After working at the Lebanon Plumbing Supply Co. for 13 years, Mark Tice purchased the controlling interest of the company in 1947. In 1975, Mark’s son Randy Tice joined the industry, launching his own controls business, Environmental Equipment Engineering Co. The two companies merged in 1982 to form APR Supply Co. Present day, APR Supply Co. has over 320 employees, the majority located at the central distribution center and corporate headquarters in Lebanon, PA.

website_title: PE Welcome | APR Supply
website_description: APR Supply Co is as a full service distributor of Plumbing, HVAC, PVF, and Hydronic supplies since 1922. We work with contractors throughout Pennsylvania, New York, New Jersey and Delaware to help our customers service their customers. You can visit anyone of our 38 branch locations or 9 showroom locations to view our products and learn more about the services that we offer. We pride ourselves on providing our customers with the highest quality products and services in the industry. APR Supply Co. has been built on a foundation of five principal, core values: Customer, Excellence, Integrity, Respect, and Results. We focus and stress putting you, our Customer first. This allows us to provide you with the correct product or service in a timely manner. Through our efforts within Excellence, our central distribution center is able to offer you next day delivery, a large inventory, and an order accuracy rate of over 99.5%. By operating with Integrity and Respect, we establish and maintain great relationships with our customers and our vendors by showcasing our strong work ethic and willingness to do the right thing. By combining our efforts in putting the Customer first, providing product and service Excellence, and operating with Integrity and Respect, we achieve the Results that you are looking for, and we achieve our company mission: Creating Enthusiastic Customers! APR Supply Co. is a third generation wholesaler that grew from the development of the Lebanon Plumbing Supply Co. After working at the Lebanon Plumbing Supply Co. for 13 years, Mark Tice purchased the controlling interest of the company in 1947. In 1975, Mark’s son Randy Tice joined the industry, launching his own controls business, Environmental Equipment Engineering Co. The two companies merged in 1982 to form APR Supply Co. Present day, APR Supply Co. has over 320 employees, the majority located at the central distribution center and corporate headquarters in Lebanon, PA.
